#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.cov.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.tensor.cov"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.statistics.cov.cov:1 of
msgid "Estimate a covariance matrix, given data and weights."
msgstr "给定数据和权重，估计协方差矩阵。"

#: maxframe.tensor.statistics.cov.cov:3 of
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"Covariance indicates the level to which two variables vary together. If "
"we examine N-dimensional samples, :math:`X = [x_1, x_2, ... x_N]^T`, then"
" the covariance matrix element :math:`C_{ij}` is the covariance of "
":math:`x_i` and :math:`x_j`. The element :math:`C_{ii}` is the variance "
"of :math:`x_i`."
msgstr ""
"协方差表示两个变量一起变化的程度。如果我们检查 N 维样本 :math:`X = [x_1, "
"x_2, ... x_N]^T`，则协方差矩阵元素 :math:`C_{ij}` 是 :math:`x_i` 和 :math"
":`x_j` 的协方差。元素 :math:`C_{ii}` 是 :math:`x_i` 的方差。"

#: maxframe.tensor.statistics.cov.cov:9 of
msgid "See the notes for an outline of the algorithm."
msgstr "有关算法的概述，请参见说明。"

#: maxframe.tensor.statistics.cov.cov of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.statistics.cov.cov:11 of
msgid ""
"A 1-D or 2-D array containing multiple variables and observations. Each "
"row of `m` represents a variable, and each column a single observation of"
" all those variables. Also see `rowvar` below."
msgstr ""
"包含多个变量和观测值的 1-D 或 2-D 数组。`m` 的每一行代表一个变量，每一列"
"代表所有这些变量的一个观测值。另请参见下面的 `rowvar`。"

#: maxframe.tensor.statistics.cov.cov:15 of
msgid ""
"An additional set of variables and observations. `y` has the same form as"
" that of `m`."
msgstr "一组额外的变量和观测值。`y` 的形式与 `m` 相同。"

#: maxframe.tensor.statistics.cov.cov:18 of
msgid ""
"If `rowvar` is True (default), then each row represents a variable, with "
"observations in the columns. Otherwise, the relationship is transposed: "
"each column represents a variable, while the rows contain observations."
msgstr ""
"如果 `rowvar` 为 True（默认值），则每一行代表一个变量，列中是观测值。否则"
"，关系是转置的：每一列代表一个变量，行中包含观测值。"

#: maxframe.tensor.statistics.cov.cov:23 of
msgid ""
"Default normalization (False) is by ``(N - 1)``, where ``N`` is the "
"number of observations given (unbiased estimate). If `bias` is True, then"
" normalization is by ``N``. These values can be overridden by using the "
"keyword ``ddof`` in numpy versions >= 1.5."
msgstr ""
"默认归一化（False）是使用 ``(N - 1)``，其中 ``N`` 是给定的观测值数量（"
"无偏估计）。如果 `bias` 为 True，则归一化使用 ``N``。在 numpy 版本 >= 1.5"
" 中，这些值可以通过使用关键字 ``ddof`` 覆盖。"

#: maxframe.tensor.statistics.cov.cov:28 of
msgid ""
"If not ``None`` the default value implied by `bias` is overridden. Note "
"that ``ddof=1`` will return the unbiased estimate, even if both "
"`fweights` and `aweights` are specified, and ``ddof=0`` will return the "
"simple average. See the notes for the details. The default value is "
"``None``."
msgstr ""
"如果不为 ``None``，则覆盖由 `bias` 暗示的默认值。请注意，即使指定了 `"
"fweights` 和 `aweights`，``ddof=1`` 也会返回无偏估计，而 ``ddof=0`` 会"
"返回简单平均值。详见说明。默认值为 ``None``。"

#: maxframe.tensor.statistics.cov.cov:34 of
msgid ""
"1-D tensor of integer freguency weights; the number of times each "
"observation vector should be repeated."
msgstr "整数频率权重的一维张量；每个观测向量应重复的次数。"

#: maxframe.tensor.statistics.cov.cov:37 of
msgid ""
"1-D tensor of observation vector weights. These relative weights are "
"typically large for observations considered \"important\" and smaller for"
" observations considered less \"important\". If ``ddof=0`` the array of "
"weights can be used to assign probabilities to observation vectors."
msgstr ""
"观测向量权重的 1-D 张量。这些相对权重通常对于被认为 \"重要\" 的观测值较大"
"，而对于被认为不太 \"重要\" 的观测值较小。如果 ``ddof=0``，权重数组可用于"
"为观测向量分配概率。"

#: maxframe.tensor.statistics.cov.cov of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.statistics.cov.cov:43 of
msgid "**out** -- The covariance matrix of the variables."
msgstr "**out** -- 变量的协方差矩阵。"

#: maxframe.tensor.statistics.cov.cov of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.statistics.cov.cov:48 of
msgid ":py:obj:`corrcoef`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.statistics.cov.cov:49 of
msgid "Normalized covariance matrix"
msgstr "归一化的协方差矩阵"

#: maxframe.tensor.statistics.cov.cov:52 of
msgid "备注"
msgstr ""

