msgstr ""
"假设观测值位于观测数组 `m` 的列中，并且为了简洁起见，令 ``f = fweights`` "
"和 ``a = aweights``。计算加权协方差的步骤如下::"

#: maxframe.tensor.statistics.cov.cov:63 of
msgid ""
"Note that when ``a == 1``, the normalization factor ``v1 / (v1**2 - ddof "
"* v2)`` goes over to ``1 / (np.sum(f) - ddof)`` as it should."
msgstr ""
"请注意，当 ``a == 1`` 时，归一化因子 ``v1 / (v1**2 - ddof * v2)`` 会变为 "
"``1 / (np.sum(f) - ddof)``，这是正确的。"

#: maxframe.tensor.statistics.cov.cov:68 of
msgid "示例"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.statistics.cov.cov:69 of
msgid ""
"Consider two variables, :math:`x_0` and :math:`x_1`, which correlate "
"perfectly, but in opposite directions:"
msgstr "考虑两个变量 :math:`x_0` 和 :math:`x_1`，它们完全相关但方向相反："

#: maxframe.tensor.statistics.cov.cov:79 of
msgid ""
"Note how :math:`x_0` increases while :math:`x_1` decreases. The "
"covariance matrix shows this clearly:"
msgstr ""
"注意 :math:`x_0` 增加的同时 :math:`x_1` 减少。协方差矩阵清楚地显示了这"
"一点："

#: maxframe.tensor.statistics.cov.cov:86 of
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"Note that element :math:`C_{0,1}`, which shows the correlation between "
":math:`x_0` and :math:`x_1`, is negative."
msgstr ""
"请注意元素 :math:`C_{0,1}` 显示了 :math:`x_0` 和 :math:`x_1` 之间的相关性"
"，它是负的。"

#: maxframe.tensor.statistics.cov.cov:89 of
msgid "Further, note how `x` and `y` are combined:"
msgstr "此外，请注意 `x` 和 `y` 是如何组合的："

